Cecil Morton York https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cecil_Morton_York 0 Cecil Morton York (29 April 1857 – 23 February 1935) was a British actor of the silent era.Born Cecil Morton Smith in Kensington, West London, UK, he died at age 77 in Denville Hall, Northwood, London.
